  "time_ut": 1661435362,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0db4\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0d9a \u0d89\u0db3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The principal of Ratnapura has been abusing students for some time",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of the National Child Protection Authority, Udaya Kumara Amarasinghe, said that the principal of a main school in Ratnapura district has been arrested and remanded in custody on suspicion of having seriously sexually abused a student.",
        "He also mentioned that the Child Protection Authority officers arrested this principal after a special investigation conducted on a complaint received by the authority's emergency number that the principal of a main boys' school in Ratnapura had sexually abused a student there.",
        "Mr. Amarasinghe said that during the investigation, information was revealed that this principal has been carefully bringing the students of the school to his quarters and sexually abusing them by giving them monetary rewards and various privileges.",
        "He said that after the imprisonment of the principal, other students, teachers and parents gave information against him, and investigations are being conducted to verify whether the information is true.",
        "He also said that some teachers of the school, former students, etc. are putting pressure on the witnesses to prevent them from giving such information.",
        "Mr. Udaya Kumara Amarasinghe said that there may be other children who are subjected to such abuses and some do not complain about it due to shame and fear. He also requested to inform on the number.",
        "The chairman said that the privacy and confidentiality of the children, parents and teachers who provide information will be protected and said that action will be taken against those who pressure to suppress the information."
      ],
